Resource Profile: CH ELM Patient

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-elm/StructureDefinition/ch-elm-patient Version: 1.10.0
Active as of 2025-06-23 Computable Name: ChElmPatient

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This CH ELM base profile constrains the Patient resource for the purpose of laboratory orders and test reports.

Usages:

  • Derived from this Profile: CH ELM Patient HIV, CH ELM Patient Initials and CH ELM Patient VCT
  • Use this Profile: CH ELM Document: Laboratory Report
  • Refer to this Profile: CH ELM Composition: Laboratory Report, CH ELM DiagnosticReport: Laboratory Report, CH ELM Observation Results: Laboratory, CH ELM ServiceRequest: Laboratory Order and CH ELM Specimen: Laboratory
